net.i2p.router.crypto.ratchet

Class RatchetEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.i2p.router.crypto.ratchet.RatchetEntry

  • class RatchetEntry
extends Object
    Simple object with outbound tag, key, and nonce, and an optional next keys. The object returned from SKM.consumeNextAvailableTag() to the engine encrypt.
